      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A\\in\\mathcal{M}_n(\\C)$. L'endomorphisme $f$ de $\\mathcal{M}_n(\\C)$ défini par\n$f(M) = \\mathrm{tr}(A)M+\\mathrm{tr}(M)A$ est-il diagonalisable~?",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\in\\mathcal{M}_n(\\C)\\)</span>. L’endomorphisme <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{M}_n(\\C)\\)</span> défini par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(M) = \\mathrm{tr}(A)M+\\mathrm{tr}(M)A\\)</span> est-il diagonalisable ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c20fda9b-951c-4a84-bd2d-04cad657af1d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Oui ssi $\\mathrm{tr}(A)\\ne 0$ ou $A=0$.",
        "html": "<p>Oui ssi <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathrm{tr}(A)\\ne 0\\)</span> ou <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A=0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
